&lt;p&gt;Ceph is een open-source, software-defined storage platform dat block, file en object storage combineert in één schaalbare infrastructuur. In combinatie met Proxmox VE vormt Ceph een krachtige en kostenefficiënte storage oplossing voor virtualisatieomgevingen.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Door storage direct te distribueren over meerdere nodes is er geen externe SAN of NAS nodig. Dit maakt Ceph ideaal voor moderne hyperconverged infrastructuren.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id="ceph-geïntegreerd-in-proxmox-ve"&gt;Ceph geïntegreerd in Proxmox VE&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Proxmox VE bevat native integratie met Ceph, waardoor storage direct vanuit de Proxmox webinterface beheerd kan worden.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Proxmox Support</title><link>https://mademy.nl/diensten/proxmox/proxmox-support/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/diensten/proxmox/proxmox-support/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Proxmox VE</title><link>https://mademy.nl/diensten/proxmox/proxmox-ve/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/diensten/proxmox/proxmox-ve/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Refurbished Hardware</title><link>https://mademy.nl/diensten/hardware-software/hardware/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/diensten/hardware-software/hardware/</guid><description/></item><item><title>VCF 5.x naar VCF 9, Migratie &amp; Upgrade</title><link>https://mademy.nl/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/migratie/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/migratie/</guid><description/></item><item><title>VCF Automation</title><link>https://mademy.nl/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vcf-automation/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vcf-automation/</guid><description/></item><item><title>VCF Operations</title><link>https://mademy.nl/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vcf-operations/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vcf-operations/</guid><description/></item><item><title>VMware NSX 9</title><link>https://mademy.nl/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/nsx/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/nsx/</guid><description/></item><item><title>VMware vSAN 9</title><link>https://mademy.nl/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vsan/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vsan/</guid><description/></item><item><title>VMware vSphere 9</title><link>https://mademy.nl/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vsphere/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vsphere/</guid><description/></item><item><title>vSphere Kubernetes Service (VKS)</title><link>https://mademy.nl/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vsphere-kubernetes-service/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vsphere-kubernetes-service/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>